title: Supercharger Thermal Blanket
description:
Thermal Blanket for Hellcat, Trackhawk, Durango Hellcat, Demon/Redeye provided by FAS Motorsports.

A thermal blanket for your hellcat supercharger is exactly what you need to greatly reduce the high levels of heat that the supercharger normally absorbs due to engine temperatures. If you want your supercharger to reach its full potential a thermal blanket is the perfect first step.

Blower thermal blanket ONLY.

title: 2.4L Hellcat “DOMINATOR” Race Porting Package
description: Take your Hellcat to the next level with the FAS DOMINATOR RACE 2.4L Supercharger Package. This package consists of two primary options: DOMINATOR RACE and DOMINATOR RACE ELITE. The DOMINATOR RACE is a powerful step above stock power (75 to 135+ whp). The DOMINATOR RACE ELITE package offers even more power, allowing your supercharger to support over 1100 whp! The DOMINATOR RACE ELITE package holds the record for the highest horsepower on an OEM 2.4L supercharger for the standard Hellcat platform and Trackhawk (blower only)! Recommended MAX Pulley Set up is a 2.70-2.80” upper and 10% lower Crank Pulley. NO REFUNDS ON ANY CORE PURCHASED!!! Once paid, no refunds available!!! THESE SUPERCHARGER PACKAGES HAVE A START UP WARRANTY ONLY!!! WE CAN NOT PROVE IF INSTALL WAS CORRECT OF IF PULLEY COMBO WAS WITHIN OUR SAFE RECOMMENDED RANGE.

title: 2.7L Redeye/Demon “DOMINATOR” Race Porting Package
description: Take your Hellcat to the next level with the FAS DOMINATOR RACE 2.7L Supercharger Package. We have seen gains from 75 to 135+ whp from only a DOMINATOR RACE! The DOMINATOR RACE ELITE includes everything needed for your 2.7L supercharger to support over 1100 whp! The DOMINATOR RACE ELITE package holds the record for the highest horsepower on an OEM 2.4L supercharger for the standard Hellcat platform and Trackhawk (blower only)! Shipping times vary depending on package tier and selected options. Contact us for more information. NO REFUNDS ON ANY CORE PURCHASED!!! Once paid, no refunds available!!! THESE SUPERCHARGER PACKAGES HAVE A START UP WARRANTY ONLY!!! WE CAN NOT PROVE IF INSTALL WAS CORRECT OF IF PULLEY COMBO WAS WITHIN OUR SAFE RECOMMENDED RANGE.

description: For the most aggressive rebuild, the Ceramic Race Bearing Snout Rebuild, FAS Motorsports worked directly with a bearing manufacturer to find the perfect ceramic ball bearing to hold up to all the abuse of high horse power hellcats!

description: Expect gains of 40-60rwhp on 2.4L (Hellcat / Trackhawks / Durango HC / TRX) Superchargers paired with a 108mm Throttle body, and 80-125rwhp gains on 2.7L (Demon / Redeye) Supercharger paired with a 108mm Throttle body!
